Learning Docker // Build Container Images  -- [baseado neste video do youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JDw3ZdQcv2g)   

    
executar o Dockerfile:
docker build -t my-first-container:latest .

Run container:
docker run --interactive --tty my-first-container
